data.description: Incredible dual living/multigenerational potential in this charming mid century ranch within 5 mins walking distance to Beaumont Village, 42nd Street (Pips, Fire on the Mountain); 8 mins to Alberta Arts District . All the important work is already done: newer roof, 95% furnace/AC, earthquake retrofit, updated windows, radon mitigation. 3 bed/1 bath up & 2 bed/1 bath apartment in basement w/ separate entrance & kitchenette/laundry, huge garage, pergola, & play structure! Friendly neighborhood, super walkable & 97 bike score. See 3D virtual tour & floor plan! [Home Energy Score = 4. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10187289]
